{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a83c59fc3c","title":"立即行动，制止内战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c80419a2f","index":0,"year":1943,"month":7,"day":4,"articleId":"a83c59fc3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"03d49390a9","type":"paragraph","text":"立即行动，制止内战！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"a83c59fc3c"},{"id":"50ce51ea1b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年7月4日）蒋介石调集二十余师兵力色国陕甘宁边区、战事有在数日内爆发可能，形势极度紧张。请立即将上述情况向外传播，发动制止内我运动，特别通知英、美有关人员，同时找张治中、刘变交涉制止，愈快愈好。[111943年5月，共产国际解散，使蒋介石认为反共的时机到来了，于是通不及待地制造反共宜传攻势，企图取消共产党。同时蒋合石增兵陕昔宁遗区周围，准备进攻陕甘宁边区。这是毛泽东获悉情况后八路军驻重庆办","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"a83c59fc3c"}],"page":{"id":"b855e1b00d","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"a83c59fc3c","start":86,"end":86}}}},"__N_SSG":true}